reviews.snippet:
ビリヤニの原型とも言われるウズベキスタンのプロフ。食べるのは２度目だけど、ニンジンの甘さがそう感じさせるのか、油多めの炊き込みご飯みたいだなぁと今回も思いました。
スパイスにクミン等が使われているそうだけど、エスニック感は弱めでした。
別のお店では羊肉がジャーキーみたいだったけど、こちらのは柔らかく食べやすいお肉でした。
セットのドリンクが３種類から選べて、現地でポピュラーなアイランというヨーグルト飲料にしたけど、塩分のせいかクセ強めでした。量がたっぷりなので正直ツラかった…。
オーダーはモバイルオーダーで、各種キャッシュレス決済に対応しています。

extracted_snippet.translated:
Uzbek plov is said to be the prototype of biryani. This was my second time eating it, and once again I thought it tasted like oily rice, perhaps because of the sweetness of the carrots.
Apparently cumin and other spices were used, but the ethnic feel was weak.
At another restaurant the lamb was like jerky, but here it was soft and easy to eat.
There were three drinks to choose from with the set, and I chose ayran, a yogurt drink that's popular locally, but it had a strong flavor, probably due to the salt. The portion was so generous that it was honestly quite hard to eat...
Ordering is done via mobile, and various cashless payment methods are available.

reviews.snippet:
Wir waren leider etwas enttäuscht. Die samsas waren am besten, die kababs waren auch gut nur die Portionen waren bei der shish kabab platte etwas klein und dafür teuer. Das Brot war alt und hart. Die Beilagen waren sehr wenig und haben nicht geschmeckt. Zu jedem Gericht kam eine rote Soße die leider 0 von 10 Punkten verdient hat.
Unsere Bananenmilch war viel zu süß und der ayran viel zu salzig. Beide kann ich nicht empfehlen. Das Geländer bei der Treppe nach oben ist extrem klebrig und sollte bitte dringend gereinigt werden.

Ansonsten das Personal war freundlich, die samsas waren sehr gut und die Gebetsecke war gut. Jedoch sollte man an der roten Soße und den Beilagen etwa verbessern und unbedingt das Salz und Zucker in den Getränken verringern.

extracted_snippet.translated:
Unfortunately we were a bit disappointed. The samsas were the best, the kababs were also good, but the portions of the shish kabab plate were a bit small and expensive. The bread was old and hard. The side dishes were very few and didn't taste good. Every dish came with a red sauce which unfortunately earned 0 out of 10 points.
Our banana milk was way too sweet and the ayran way too salty. I can't recommend both. The railing on the stairs upstairs is extremely sticky and should be cleaned urgently.

Otherwise the staff was friendly, the samsas were very good and the prayer corner was good. However, you should improve the red sauce and the side dishes and definitely reduce the salt and sugar in the drinks.

reviews.snippet:
シシカバブが好きなのと評価も高いので初来訪。
ランチセットでケバブ+ナンを選択。オーダーはQRコードを読み込んでスマホでオーダーするスタイル。店員さんにとっても客側にとってもノンストレスかつスムーズでいいと思います。
さてお食事ですが、チキンのケバブとビーフ？ラム？が小さ目のハーフナンの上に乗っていました。チキンは美味しかったのですが、もう一方のお肉は、ひどい筋肉で噛んでも噛んでも噛みきれず....お行儀悪いけれど飲み込めなかったので吐き出してしまいました。残念。
サラダは見た通りのお味。ヨーグルトのスープはさっぱりしていてよかったです。
女子でも物足りなく感じる量なので男性だとこの量では足りないかも。
近くに行ったらまた違ったメニューも食べてみたいですが、わざわざ出向くかどうかは微妙なところ。
スタッフはとっても親切で気持ちの良い対応をして下さいました！

I came here for the first time because I like shish kebab and it's highly rated.
Choose kebab + naan for lunch set. Ordering is done by scanning a QR code and using your smartphone. I think it should be stress-free and smooth for both staff and customers.
Now, about the meal, chicken kebab and beef? Ram? was on top of a small half naan. The chicken was delicious, but I couldn't chew the other piece of meat because of my terrible muscles... It was bad manners, but I couldn't swallow it, so I spat it out. disappointing.
The salad tastes as good as it looks. The yogurt soup was refreshing and good.
Even girls feel unsatisfied with this amount, so this amount may not be enough for men.
I'd like to try a different menu if I go nearby, but I'm not sure if I'll go out of my way or not.
The staff were very kind and made me feel comfortable!
